-- India May Charge HSBC With Aiding Tax Evaders, PTI Reports
-- B y   S i d d h a r t h   P h i l i p
-- 2012-03-28T14:45:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-28/india-may-charge-hsbc-with-aiding-tax-evaders-pti-reports.html
India ’s income tax department is
considering prosecuting  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  for helping Indians
hide money overseas, the Press Trust of India reported, citing
people it didn’t identify.  Rajesh Joshi, a spokesman for HSBC in Mumbai, declined to
comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
